d=L4x%2BeUtBej3jPi%2FfB6OFQf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=513a04e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=syria+property+for+sale&amp;oq=syria+property+for+sale</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=syria+real+estate&amp;oq=syria+real+estate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dsyria%2Breal%2Bestate%26oq%3Dsyria%2Breal%2Bestate&d=L4x%2BeUtBej3jPi%2FfB6OFQf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=5d197ea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/search?q=syria+real+estate&amp;oq=syria+real+estate</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叙利亞人平均收入：<br />\n每月43524元叙利亞幣（85美元）<br />\n租金：1房單位94254叙利亞幣（184美元）<br />\n<br />\n樓價（每平方米）：112萬叙利亞幣（2160美元）<br />\n<br />\n樓價（每平方呎）：10.4萬叙利亞幣（201美元）（1560港元）<br />\n<br />\n據估計，在過去幾年，在叙利亞，雙方曾投下超過10000牧炸彈以上。<br />\n<br />\n打緊杖的地方，都要成1560蚊一呎<br />\n<br />\n當年沙士，香港嘉湖山莊都係賣緊1800蚊一呎<br />\n<br />\n你話港樓算唔算貴？"},{"pid":"fcfa5d553bd41afa414681c730f4c0510dcf0320","tid":642614,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T04:07:06.000Z","msg":"打仗前，大馬士革係大城市，一d都唔輸蝕。"},{"pid":"bcec7fa6d0260413105308125a36aed796d7f2e6","tid":642614,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcfa5d553bd41afa414681c730f4c0510dcf0320","tid":642614,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T04:07:06.000Z","msg":"打仗前，大馬士革係大城市，一d都唔輸蝕。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T04:19:07.000Z","msg":"打杖到壓不了樓價<br />\n<br />\n連登仔想樓價大跌，難了"},{"pid":"25dd6cc0c272b4462d47db1bb42ed79f513bcd65","tid":642614,"uid":172787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T04:21:55.000Z","msg":"打仗仲要返工？"},{"pid":"502d5ccfa7edb6dfae29a8b7b1a3bbbb3b57bc9b","tid":642614,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25dd6cc0c272b4462d47db1bb42ed79f513bcd65","tid":642614,"uid":172787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T04:21:55.000Z","msg":"打仗仲要返工？"},"ci